0.6.0: 2010/19/12
     - fixed default DOCUMENT_ROOT and VIRTUAL_BASE (Apache's DOCUMENT_ROOT is without a trailing slash by default)
     - added mime.types file support requested by Hanz Makmur <makmur@cs.rutgers.edu>
